{"tid":385453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓核試  美：放寬南韓飛彈限制","createTime":"2017-09-03T08:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T11:07:49.000Z","uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c706bc9b685e16e93c3cea2ff7333cd3d0182c1","tid":385453,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:41:39.000Z","msg":"北韓今日疑似核試爆，兩度造成地震傳出，南韓國會防務委員會指出，北韓此次第6次核試驗，達到1945年日本長崎核彈的4.5至5倍威力，相當於黃色炸藥（TNT）10萬噸引爆。北韓官方已在今日下午証實，核爆測試成功。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普與南韓總統文在寅核試後通電話，就朝鮮半島情勢交換意見，兩人同意修改「美韓飛彈指導準則」。<br />\n<br />\n川普表示，同意美國對南韓的數十億美元軍售計畫。修改飛彈指導準則將使南韓能擺脫限制，增加飛彈彈頭重量與射程，增強南韓因應北韓挑釁的自主嚇阻力量。川普表示，運用最大程度的制裁及施壓令北韓回到談判桌，對和平解決北韓核議題至關重要。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/sep/3/images/bigPic/600_111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Fsep%2F3%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F600_111.jpg&h=045cf1dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b79cec08ebe128f7df78bbfea28275b49668de75","tid":385453,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:45:52.000Z","msg":"等睇中國口交部強烈反對"},{"pid":"9bc629f72b59a25bec47ee8f5f8d59c75753adb7","tid":385453,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a372ca7d93ab6491a266525ab4e63c84ed6eea77","tid":385453,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:53:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38fd7e94b163c0a68b7c6f64e6c2a5885da97588","tid":385453,"uid":3117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:23:54.000Z","msg":"之前又講到朝鮮敢核試就打硬，依家影都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d295cfff2d8addff43f41373d7c641febe2e1357","tid":385453,"uid":124048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:31:50.000Z","msg":"怕怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ddfd8c2d68dd